data.description: Destiny Homes presents their Amana home plan, approximately 90 days dig to completion. This two story plan features three bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and 1273 sq ft of finished space. Shotgun style open concept living area hosts the dining, kitchen, and living room. The dining sits at the front of the home while the kitchen features quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and eat in kitchen. The kitchen opens up to the large living room with huge picture windows and an electric fireplace. Half bath is located off the turnback staircase which leads to three large bedrooms upstairs, 2 baths, and laundry. There is a long list of standard features not often found at this price point, including electric fireplace, energy efficiency, SMART Home Automation, and 2x6 construction. All appliances included. Ask about $2,000 in closing costs provided by preferred lender.
